		<h1 class="entry-title">Felt Bobs</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Here&#8217;s how you mount the felt bobs. They should lightly rub against the inside of the cradle runners. Although the installation for these kinda sucks (meaning, the screw locations aren&#8217;t marked) the end result is really nice. You can remove the cradle and rest it on a table top, and the cradle will not roll away.<br />
